                and distribute your content in relation to our Services.
              </p>

              <h3>6.2 Content Responsibility</h3>
              <p>You are fully responsible for:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>All content you post</li>
                <li>Ensuring you have the right to post the content</li>
                <li>That the content does not violate third-party rights</li>
                <li>That the content complies with these Terms</li>
              </ul>

              <h3>6.3 Moderation</h3>
              <p>
                We reserve the right to review, moderate, or remove any content
                we deem inappropriate, although we have no obligation to do so.
              </p>

              <h3>6.4 Reports</h3>
              <p>
                If you find content that violates these Terms, you may report it
                through our support channels.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section id="intellectual-property">
              <h2>7. Intellectual Property</h2>

              <h3>7.1 Our Content</h3>
              <p>
                The Services and all their original content, features, and
                functionality are owned by SECiD and are protected by copyright,
                trademarks, and other intellectual property laws.
              </p>

              <h3>7.2 License to Use</h3>
              <p>
