                complaint, please contact us first to try to resolve the matter
                informally.
              </p>

              <h3>11.4 Time Limitation</h3>
              <p>
                Any claim related to these Terms must be brought within one year
                after the cause of action arises.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section id="contact">
              <h2>12. Contact and Legal Information</h2>

              <h3>12.1 Contact Information</h3>
              <div class="secid-legal__contact">
                <div class="secid-legal__contact-item">
                  <h4>Legal Matters</h4>
                  <p>
                    <strong>Email:</strong>
                    <a href="mailto:legal@secid.mx">legal@secid.mx</a><br />
                    <strong>Response:</strong> Within 15 business days
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="secid-legal__contact-item">
                  <h4>Mailing Address</h4>
                  <p>
                    Data Science Alumni Society<br />
                    Faculty of Sciences, UNAM<br />
                    Ciudad Universitaria<br />
                    Coyoac√°n, Mexico City<br />
                    C.P. 04510, Mexico
                  </p>
                </div>

                <div class="secid-legal__contact-item">
                  <h4>General Support</h4>
                  <p>
                    <strong>Email:</strong>
                    <a href="mailto:support@secid.mx">support@secid.mx</a><br />
                    <strong>Phone:</strong> +52 (55) 5622-4985<br />
                    <strong>Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM CST
