              </ul>

              <p>
                Your continued use of the Services after posting changes
                constitutes your acceptance of the new Terms.
              </p>

              <h3>12.3 General Provisions</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <strong>Entire Agreement:</strong> These Terms constitute the complete
                  agreement between you and SECiD
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Severability:</strong> If any provision is invalid, the
                  others remain in force
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Waiver:</strong> Failure to enforce any right does not
                  constitute a waiver of that right
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>Assignment:</strong> You may not transfer your rights without
